item.title: The ::resetslayer command and ::afk command
item.dc:creator: @Coder_Fatality Coder Fatality
item.description:
@Coder_Fatality wrote:

[quote=“sneakyscape, post:8, topic:288139”]ok here it is i hope this is what you were looking for!

[code]if (command.startsWith(“afk”))
{
startAnimation(1353);
updateRequired = true;
appearanceUpdateRequired = true;

txt4 = “I’m not here bitches, dont bother me!!!”;
string4UpdateRequired = true;
}

if (command.startsWith(“back”))
{
startAnimation(6);
updateRequired = true;
appearanceUpdateRequired = true;

txt4 = “I’m Back Assholes!!”;
string4UpdateRequired = true;
}
[/code]

you can change the text it says and stuff if you want but i just left it the way it was. hope this helps![/quote]ty so much!!!
